POSTMAN STRUCTURE (PRODUCTION-READY)

Bitcoin Treasury Platform (Prod)
├── Auth
├── Treasury
├── Wallets
├── Transactions
├── Performance
├── Prospectus
├── Compliance
└── Integrations
Base URL
https://api.yourdomain.com
Auth
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
________________________________________
1. AUTH MODULE
Login
POST /auth/login
{
  "email": "cfo@institution.com",
  "password": "********"
}
Response
{
  "accessToken": "jwt-token",
  "role": "CFO"
}
________________________________________
2. TREASURY MODULE
Treasury Overview
GET /treasury/overview
Response
{
  "btcHoldings": 312.45,
  "averageCost": 42350,
  "marketValueUSD": 19600000,
  "allocation": {
    "btc": 68,
    "fiat": 32
  }
}
________________________________________
Treasury Policy
POST /treasury/policy
{
  "btcAllocationTarget": "60-75%",
  "reviewFrequency": "Annual",
  "maxDrawdownTolerance": "-45%"
}
________________________________________
3. WALLET MODULE (INSTITUTIONAL)
List Wallets
GET /wallets
{
  "wallets": [
    {
      "type": "Cold Storage",
      "policy": "3-of-5 multisig",
      "balanceBTC": 280.12
    }
  ]
}
________________________________________
Create Wallet
POST /wallets/create
{
  "type": "Cold",
  "multisig": {
    "m": 3,
    "n": 5
  }
}
________________________________________
4. TRANSACTION MODULE (NON-TRADING)
Initiate Transfer
POST /transactions/send
{
  "toAddress": "bc1qexample",
  "amountBTC": 2.5,
  "purpose": "Treasury rebalancing"
}
Response
{
  "txId": "btc_tx_hash",
  "status": "PENDING_APPROVAL"
}
________________________________________
Approve Transaction
POST /transactions/approve
{
  "txId": "btc_tx_hash"
}
________________________________________
Transaction History
GET /transactions/history
________________________________________
5. PERFORMANCE MODULE (CORE)
Performance Overview
GET /performance/overview
{
  "period": "YTD",
  "unrealizedPnL": {
    "usd": 6420000,
    "percent": 48.6
  },
  "btcVsFiatBenchmark": "+31%",
  "maxDrawdown": "-38%"
}
________________________________________
Performance Timeline
GET /performance/timeline
{
  "monthly": [
    { "month": "Jan", "valueUSD": 14200000 },
    { "month": "Feb", "valueUSD": 15800000 }
  ]
}
________________________________________
Strategy Metrics
GET /performance/strategy
{
  "strategy": "Long-term Bitcoin Treasury",
  "timeHorizon": "5-10 years",
  "inflationHedgeScore": 8.9,
  "custodyModel": "Cold multisig"
}
________________________________________
6. PROSPECTUS MODULE (INSTITUTIONAL)
Prospectus Summary
GET /prospectus/summary
{
  "entity": "PT Bitcoin Treasury Global",
  "objective": "Capital preservation & inflation hedge",
  "btcAllocationTarget": "60–75%",
  "custody": "Institutional cold multisig"
}
________________________________________
Prospectus Performance Disclosure
GET /prospectus/performance
{
  "btcCAGR": "42%",
  "relativeOutperformance": "+35%",
  "stressScenarios": [
    "BTC -50% → Treasury -32%"
  ]
}
________________________________________
Generate Board / Investor Report
POST /prospectus/report
{
  "audience": "Board",
  "period": "FY2025",
  "format": "PDF"
}
________________________________________
7. COMPLIANCE MODULE
Audit Logs
GET /compliance/audit-logs
{
