PRODUCTION POSITIONING (IMPORTANT)
Postman ini menunjukkan platform Anda adalah:
- Treasury system (NOT exchange)
- Board & regulator friendly
- Audit-first & compliance-first
- Comparable to public company BTC disclosures

Sangat cocok untuk:
•	Bank partner
•	Institutional investor
•	Auditor
•	Regulator
•	Enterprise client due diligence



